        <mxCell id="title3" value="&lt;b&gt;C2 Container Diagram: Task Board with Security Components&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;ENGSE207 Week 12 - ปรับปรุงจาก Week 6 Docker Architecture" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontSize=14;" vertex="1" parent="1">
